4Geeks Academy offers a Cybersecurity Bootcamp designed for individuals with no prior knowledge, aiming to equip them with essential skills to become cybersecurity specialists. The program spans 16 weeks, featuring three live online classes each week, with a maximum class size of 16 participants. Students will gain foundational knowledge in Windows, Linux, network, and server administration, along with advanced skills in cloud security, penetration testing, and risk management. The course is available in English and Spanish, and participants will receive an Official 4Geeks Completion Certificate upon completion. 

